Package: chanwer
Title: ChanWe Visual Themes for Quarto Workflows
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Chanwe",
           family = "Team",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "team@chanwe.example")
Description: Brand-consistent themes, color palettes, and utilities for
    ChanWe reporting workflows across ggplot2, gt, reactable, and
    highcharter, with Quarto-ready styling tokens for HTML, Typst PDF,
    and PPTX outputs.
